fix: improve language detection logic - any Chinese character means Chinese

Breaking Change:
- Changed language detection from "20% threshold" to "any Chinese character"
- Previous logic: chineseRatio > 0.2 → Chinese
- New logic: chineseCount > 0 → Chinese

Rationale:
- Technical documents in Chinese often contain English terminology
- Examples: "Python 爬虫", "HTTP 请求", "API 设计" are all Chinese documents
- If user includes any Chinese character, they likely want Chinese output
- More intuitive and user-friendly behavior

Examples:
- "Crawler 引擎" → Chinese (was English with 20% threshold)
- "Python 爬虫" → Chinese ✓
- "HTTP 请求优化" → Chinese ✓
- "Pure English Title" → English ✓

Files Changed:
- lib/i18n.js: Simplified detectLanguage() function
- MULTILINGUAL.md: Updated documentation
